        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "PORTABLE COMPACT BUTANE TORCH: ToolTreaux's butane pencil torch with adjustable and precise flame control is an essential tool to keep in your toolbox; it's highly versatile, cordless, compact, portable, easy to use and refill, and will reach up to temperatures of 1300 degrees Celsius or 2370 degrees Fahrenheit",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "CRAFT SUPPLIES ESSENTIAL: Multipurpose hobby tools are always a valuable addition to your arsenal of craft supplies! This butane torch can be used for soldering, jewelry design or repair, woodworking, culinary work, electrical and will melt many materials like silver, gold, tin, aluminum, copper and more",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "REFILLABLE BUTANE TORCH: Easy to maintain, refill and use on the go! The ToolTreaux pencil style butane torch is easily refillable using a standard butane lighter canister (sold separately)",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "BRASS AND ALUMINUM CONSTRUCTION: The butane torch or pencil torch features an aluminum body and brass control valve, neck and tip; these are durable, reliable materials that make this versatile tool able to stand up to lots of wear and tear",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
